zhao.algorithmMagic.integrator.launcher

类 ImageRenderingMarLauncher<T extends Matrix<?,?,?,?,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • zhao.algorithmMagic.integrator.launcher.ImageRenderingMarLauncher<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - 需要提供给集成器的矩阵对象数据类型。 2023/2/9 13:59
    所有已实现的接口:
    ImageRenderingLauncher<T>, Launcher<ImageRenderingLauncher<T>>

    public final class ImageRenderingMarLauncher<T extends Matrix<?,?,?,?,?>>
extends Object
implements ImageRenderingLauncher<T>
    矩阵绘图集成器，其转为矩阵对象定制，能够将大部分函数配置成与矩阵可以适配的功能，减少了实现启动器的步骤.

    Matrix drawing integrator, which is converted to matrix object customization, can configure most functions as functions that can adapt to the matrix, reducing the steps to implement the starter.

    作者:
    赵凌宇
